"""
Enhanced Mechanism Dictionary Tab - Professional mechanism catalog with macanism aesthetics

This tab provides a comprehensive mechanism reference system with the professional
quality and visual design of github.com/AlanSynn/macanism. Features include:

- Professional mechanism catalog with live interactive previews
- Real-time search and filtering with intelligent suggestions
- Educational content integration (theory, applications, design guidelines)
- Export capabilities for mechanism configurations and data
- Interactive parameter exploration with live visualization
- Professional engineering aesthetics with consistent grid system

The tab serves as the authoritative reference hub that complements the interactive
workshop experience of the Mechanism Foundry.
"""

